> 
> ***Beak.*** *Melee Weapon Attack:* +6 to hit, reach 5 ft., one target.
*Hit:* 7 (1d6 + 4) piercing damage.
>
> ***Claws.*** *Melee Weapon Attack:* +6 to hit, reach 5 ft., one target.
*Hit:* 9 (2d4 + 4) slashing damage.
>
> ***Screech (1/Day).*** The gryphon emits a feral screech. Each creature within 20 feet of it that can hear it must succeed on a DC 13 Constitution saving throw or be frightened until the end of the gryphon's next turn.

