> ## Keeper of the Grove <!-- https://wc5e-cr-calculator.frogvall.com/?1;17;221;8;16;62;9;41;9;41;9;0;0;0;0;0;0;;;;;3;;;;;;;;;;1;;;;;;;;10;;;;;; -->
>*Large fey, lawful neutral*
> ___
> - **Armor Class** 17 (natural armor)
> - **Hit Points** 221 (26d10 + 78)
> - **Speed** 40 ft.
>___
>|STR|DEX|CON|INT|WIS|CHA|
>|:---:|:---:|:---:|:---:|:---:|:---:|
>|14 (+2)|16 (+3)|16 (+3)|12 (+1)|18 (+4)|14 (+2)|
>___
> - **Skills** Nature +5, Perception +8, Survival +8
> - ***Damage Resistances*** lightning, poison
> - **Senses** darkvision 60ft., passive Perception 18
> - **Languages** Common, Darnassian
> - **Challenge** 10 (5,900 XP)
> ___
> ***Forest Walk.*** The keeper ignores difficult terrain in forests.
> 
> ***Speak with Beasts and Plants.*** The keeper of the grove can communicate with beasts and plants as if they shared a language.
>
> ***Unearthly Grace.*** The keeper of the grove adds its Charisma modifier on all saving throws and its AC.
>
> ***Spellcasting.*** The keeper of the grove is a 12th-level spellcaster. Its spellcasting ability is Wisdom (spell save DC 16, +8 to hit with spell attacks). It has the following druid spells prepared:
>
> Cantrips (at will): *druidcraft, resistance, solar wrath*
> <br> 1st level (4 slots): *beast bond, detect poison and <br>    disease, entangle, cure wounds*
> <br> 2nd level (3 slots): *beast sense, locate animals and <br>    plants, spike growth*
> <br> 3rd level (3 slots): *mass healing word, revivify, plant <br>    growth*
> <br> 4th level (3 slots): *conjure woodland beings, grasping <br>    vine, guardian of nature*
> <br> 5th level (2 slots): *tree stride, wrath of nature*
> <br> 6th level (1 slot): *wall of thorns*
>
> ### Actions
> 
> ***Barbed Whip.***  *Melee Weapon Attack:* +7 to hit, reach 20 ft., one target. *Hit:* 13 (3d6 + 3) piercing damage, and if the creature is large or smaller, it is pulled or pushed up to 10 feet at any direction.
>
> ***Hooves.*** *Melee Weapon Attack:* +5 to hit, reach 5 ft., one target. *Hit:* 7 (2d6) bludgeoning damage.
>
> ### Reactions
>
> ***Thorns Aura.*** When a creature within 5 feet of the keeper of the grove hits it with a melee attack, the keeper can use its reaction to deal 9 (2d8) force damage to them.


